- Module: import SmartyView for clearCache
- added {subview} smarty function
- SmartyView: modified the hooks: added preSubviewRender which is the first hook, used to be preRender. preRender is now after the rendering of the subviews.
- SmartyView: implemented the return boolean in the render method
- SmartyView: renamed setView and getViews to setSubview and getSubviews
- SmartyView: changed default compile directory to application/data/cache/smarty/compile
- Module: implemented clear cache event
- ResourceHandler: added cache to resource handler
- ResourceHandler: using filesystem\Browser to find the template paths
- HtmlSmartyView: don't parse local anchors (eg #detail) in HtmlSmartyView